CONTEXT GibraltarBB IN ENGLISH
-- Compile-time entry point: the relations (main.adl) plus the population (population.adl),
-- both pulled in with INCLUDE. Compiling this file exercises the Ampersand compiler's
-- (Haskell) population importer:
--
--     ampersand check model/GibraltarBB.adl
--
-- The runtime counterpart imports e2e/GibraltarBB.yml into a running prototype instead;
-- see this project's README.
INCLUDE "main.adl"
INCLUDE "population.adl"
ENDCONTEXT
